<section id="services-hero-532"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-11.jpeg" height="775" width="1920" fetchpriority="high"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-card"><div class="cs-heading-group"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Green Year-Round. No Water.</span><h1 class="cs-title">Artificial Turf Installation in <span class="cs-color">Las Cruces, NM</span></h1></div><p class="cs-text">Real grass loses the fight in the Chihuahuan Desert. Artificial turf gives you a green yard that holds up to 100°F summers, dog traffic, and the city watering ordinance, without mowing, fertilizing, or rising water bills. We install pet-safe, UV-stabilized synthetic grass on properly compacted bases that won't sink or shift. 19 years in business. 500+ projects installed. Workmanship guarantee.</p><div class="cs-button-group"><a href="/contact/" class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button">Schedule Free Estimate</a> <a href="tel:575-635-8883" class="cs-phone-button"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="18" width="18" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div></div></div></section><section id="services-intro-109"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern cs-fern-right"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern cs-fern-left"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-row"><img alt="Pet-safe artificial turf backyard installation by Brainard's Greenscapes in Las Cruces" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-12.jpeg" height="570" width="480" loading="lazy"><div class="cs-content"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> What Is Artificial Turf?</span><h2 class="cs-title">Synthetic Grass Built for the Desert Sun</h2><p class="cs-text">Artificial turf is a UV-stabilized polyethylene fiber tufted into a perforated drainage backing. Installed over a properly graded and compacted base with a weed barrier and the right infill, it looks like grass, drains like rock, and lasts 15 to 20 years with almost no maintenance. We install landscape-grade and pet-grade synthetic grass for backyards, front yards, patios, dog runs, and putting greens across Las Cruces.</p><ul class="cs-bullets"><li>No watering. No mowing. No fertilizing. No edging.</li><li>Stays green at 105°F and through 20°F winter nights.</li><li>Pet-safe options with antimicrobial infill that handles dog urine.</li><li>Drains faster than the real lawn it replaced.</li><li>15 to 20 year lifespan with manufacturer UV warranty.</li></ul><div class="cs-button-group"><a href="/contact/" class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button">Schedule Free Estimate</a> <a href="tel:575-635-8883" class="cs-phone-button"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="13" width="13" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div></div></div><ul class="cs-card-group"><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-landscaping.svg" height="56" width="56" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Backyard Lawns</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Full backyard turf installs that replace dead grass or rock with a soft, green play surface kids and pets actually use.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-landscape-design.svg" height="56" width="56" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Pet &amp; Dog Areas</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Pet-grade turf with antimicrobial infill and perforated drainage that drinks dog urine and rinses clean with a hose.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-hardscaping.svg" height="56" width="56" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Patio &amp; Front Yards</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Inset turf panels around pavers, narrow side yards, and HOA-friendly front-yard installs that pass curb-appeal review.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-xeriscaping.svg" height="56" width="56" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Putting Greens</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Backyard nylon putting greens with realistic ball roll, contoured cups, and a fringe collar of standard turf around the green.</p></li></ul></div></section><section id="services-process-148"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> How We Work</span><h2 class="cs-title">Our 5-Step Artificial Turf Install Process</h2></div><div class="cs-grid-wrap"><ul class="cs-card-group"><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Free On-Site Estimate</h3><p class="cs-item-text">We measure the area, talk turf grade, drainage, pets, and use, and write you an itemized quote. No obligation, no pressure.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Removal &amp; Grading</h3><p class="cs-item-text">We strip existing grass, rock, or dirt, regrade for proper drainage, and run a slight slope away from the house.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Base &amp; Weed Barrier</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Three to four inches of crushed stone, compacted in lifts to 90% density. Weed barrier on top so nothing pushes through later.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Turf, Seam &amp; Infill</h3><p class="cs-item-text">Roll out, trim, seam with turf adhesive and seam tape, anchor the perimeter, then power-broom in silica sand or zeolite infill.</p></li><li class="cs-item"><div class="cs-icon-wrap"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb.svg" height="40" width="40" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy"></div><h3 class="cs-item-title">Walkthrough &amp; Care Plan</h3><p class="cs-item-text">We walk the install with you, hand off a maintenance plan, and book a free 30-day check-in. Workmanship guarantee starts day one.</p></li></ul><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-down.svg" height="184" width="168" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-vine cs-vine-1"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-up.svg" height="184" width="168" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-vine cs-vine-2"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-down.svg" height="184" width="168" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-vine cs-vine-3"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-up.svg" height="184" width="168" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-vine cs-vine-4"></div></div></section><section id="services-signs-870"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-content"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Reasons to Switch</span><h2 class="cs-title">Why Las Cruces Homeowners Switch to Artificial Turf</h2><p class="cs-text">Most artificial turf calls we get start with one of these. Real turf isn't the answer for every yard, especially in the desert. A proper synthetic install solves the underlying problem instead of patching it every spring.</p></div><div class="cs-button-group"><a href="/contact/" class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button">Tell Us About Your Yard</a> <a href="tel:575-635-8883" class="cs-phone-button"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/phone.svg" height="13" width="13" aria-hidden="true"> (575) 635-8883</a></div><ul class="cs-signs"><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Brown, Patchy Lawn Every Summer</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">Cool-season turf can't survive 100°F afternoons and 10 inches of annual rainfall. Synthetic stays green July through September.</p></li><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Tired of Mowing in 100°F Heat</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">A backyard turf install eliminates mowing, edging, and trimming. Most homeowners spend less than 15 minutes a month on upkeep.</p></li><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Dog Urine Spots and Worn Trails</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">Pet-grade turf drains urine straight through, rinses clean with a hose, and stops the dead-spot cycle for good.</p></li><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Climbing Summer Water Bills</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">Replacing a turf lawn with synthetic typically cuts outdoor water use 80% or more. The savings show up by the second billing cycle.</p></li><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Address-Parity Watering Days</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">Las Cruces restricts when you can water. Synthetic turf needs none, so address parity, Monday lockout, and the daytime window all stop applying.</p></li><li class="cs-sign"><h3 class="cs-sign-title">Grass Won't Grow There Anyway</h3><p class="cs-sign-text">Heavy shade, narrow side yards, slopes, compacted soil, and high-traffic zones almost never grow turf. Synthetic works where seed and sod fail.</p></li></ul></div><img alt="Brainard's Greenscapes synthetic grass lawn install in Las Cruces" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-21.jpeg" height="1029" width="616" loading="lazy"></div></section><section id="services-region-450"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Turf Grades</span><h2 class="cs-title">The Right Turf for the Job</h2></div><div class="cs-body"><p class="cs-text">Not every artificial turf is the same. Pile height, blade shape, face weight, infill type, and backing all change how the lawn looks, drains, and feels underfoot. We carry residential landscape-grade, pet-grade, and putting-green turfs from manufacturers with documented UV warranties and lead-free certifications.</p><p class="cs-text"><strong>Landscape-grade turf:</strong> 1.5 to 2 inch pile, soft hand, realistic blade colors. Best for full-yard backyard installs and front yards. Typical UV warranty 10 to 15 years.</p><p class="cs-text"><strong>Pet-grade turf:</strong> shorter pile, denser face weight, fully perforated drainage backing rated 30+ inches per hour. Pairs with antimicrobial zeolite infill that captures urine ammonia.</p><p class="cs-text"><strong>Putting-green turf:</strong> nylon fiber, very short pile, designed for true ball roll. We install greens with contoured cups, fringe collars, and a sand-filled rolling surface tuned for desert use.</p><p class="cs-text"><strong>Playground turf:</strong> shock-pad underlayment for fall protection, IPEMA-tested fiber, perfect for backyard play structures and trampoline zones.</p><p class="cs-text"><strong>Infill choices:</strong> rounded silica sand for residential, zeolite for pet areas, coated cooling sands for full-sun installs. We size infill weight to your turf's face weight, not a one-size-fits-all bag count.</p><p class="cs-text">Bring a paint chip or a piece of stone from your patio to the consultation, and we'll match the turf blade color and base color to your hardscape. Synthetic turf is widely treated as a water-wise alternative to lawn in the Chihuahuan Desert because it eliminates outdoor irrigation entirely. We can walk you through the <a href="https://lascruces.gov/property/utilities/utility-services/water-conservation/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Las Cruces Water Conservation Program</a> at the consultation.</p><a href="/contact/" class="cs-button-solid cs-nav-button">Pick Your Turf</a></div><img alt="Premium artificial turf installation by Brainard's Greenscapes in Las Cruces, NM" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-1.webp" height="907" width="440" loading="lazy"></div></section><section id="services-why-353"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/leaves-pattern.jpeg" height="1777" width="1920" loading="lazy"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Why Choose Us</span><h2 class="cs-title">Why Las Cruces Trusts Brainard’s with Their Turf</h2><p class="cs-intro">Most turf failures we get called to fix are base-prep failures. The seam pulled apart, the surface settled and rippled, the weeds came up underneath, the drainage backed up. Get the base right, and the turf lasts 20 years. We've installed 500+ landscape projects across the Mesilla Valley and back every install with a workmanship guarantee.</p></div><div class="cs-gallery" aria-hidden="true"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-26.jpeg" height="594" width="460" loading="lazy"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/brainards-artificial-turf-32.jpeg" height="439" width="330" loading="lazy"></div><ul class="cs-feature-list"><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Base Prep That Lasts</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Three to four inches of crushed stone, compacted in lifts to 90% density. Proper drainage slope. Weed barrier on top. The turf only lasts as long as the base under it.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">In-House Crews, Start to Finish</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Same company quotes the job and installs it. No subcontractor markup, no quality drift, no finger-pointing if a seam needs to be re-glued.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Manufacturer-Backed Turf Only</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">UV-stabilized turf with lead-free certifications and 10 to 15 year fade warranties. We can show you spec sheets so you know exactly what's going down.</p></li><li class="cs-feature"><div class="cs-feature-head"><h3 class="cs-feature-title">Workmanship Guarantee</h3><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-feature-arrow"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></div><p class="cs-feature-text">Seams, anchoring, and base work carry a workmanship guarantee for as long as you own the home. The turf carries its own factory UV warranty on top.</p></li></ul><a href="/contact/" class="cs-quote-button">Schedule a Free Estimate</a></div></section><section id="services-pricing-219"><div class="cs-container"><article class="cs-price-card"><h2 class="cs-price-title">What Artificial Turf Costs in Las Cruces</h2><span class="cs-price-label">Per Square Foot Installed</span> <span class="cs-price-amount"><span class="cs-price-symbol">$</span>8–$20</span><p class="cs-price-text">Standard backyard installs with landscape-grade turf and silica-sand infill come in around $10 to $14 per sq ft. Pet-grade turf with zeolite infill, premium drainage backing, or stone edging runs $14 to $18. Putting greens and full-design hardscape combos can reach $20. Most residential installs we do in Las Cruces fall between $3,000 and $25,000 total.</p><ul class="cs-price-bullets"><li>Free on-site estimate. No obligation, no pressure.</li><li>Itemized quote tied to turf grade, base depth, and edging.</li><li>Workmanship guarantee + manufacturer UV warranty.</li></ul><a href="/contact/" class="cs-price-link">Request a Pricing Estimate <svg height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></a></article><article class="cs-diff-card"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/images/leaves-pattern.jpeg" height="605" width="572" loading="lazy"><h2 class="cs-diff-title">The Brainard’s Difference</h2><ul class="cs-diff-list"><li class="cs-diff-item"><span class="cs-diff-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3 V21"></path><path d="M8 8 H16"></path></svg></span><div class="cs-diff-body"><h3 class="cs-diff-name">Faith-Centered</h3><p class="cs-diff-text">Honest pricing, clear communication. We do what we say. If a seam lifts or a corner ripples, we come back and fix it.</p></div></li><li class="cs-diff-item"><span class="cs-diff-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3 L20 6 V12 C20 16.5 16.5 20 12 21 C7.5 20 4 16.5 4 12 V6 Z"></path></svg></span><div class="cs-diff-body"><h3 class="cs-diff-name">Guaranteed Quality</h3><p class="cs-diff-text">Workmanship guarantee plus the manufacturer's UV and fade warranty layered on top.</p></div></li><li class="cs-diff-item"><span class="cs-diff-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2 C8 2 5 5 5 9 C5 14 12 22 12 22 C12 22 19 14 19 9 C19 5 16 2 12 2 Z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"></circle></svg></span><div class="cs-diff-body"><h3 class="cs-diff-name">Locally Rooted</h3><p class="cs-diff-text">In-house crews who know desert sun, monsoon drainage patterns, and Las Cruces HOA front-yard rules.</p></div></li></ul></article></div></section><section id="services-local-360"><div class="cs-container"><div class="cs-header"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/arrow-right.svg" height="10" width="48" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-topper-arrow"> Built for the Climate</span><h2 class="cs-title">Artificial Turf and the Las Cruces Water Ordinance</h2><p class="cs-text">Synthetic turf needs zero irrigation, so it sidesteps the Las Cruces watering ordinance entirely for the area you cover. Here's what that ordinance looks like, and where turf fits.</p></div><ul class="cs-local-list"><li><strong>Address parity:</strong> even-numbered addresses water Tue / Thu / Sat. Odd-numbered water Wed / Fri / Sun. Turf needs no watering days.</li><li><strong>No watering Mondays.</strong> A non-issue for synthetic turf, since you only rinse it when you choose to.</li><li><strong>April 1 to Sept 30:</strong> no watering 10 a.m. to 6 p.m. Synthetic turf has no daytime restriction at all.</li><li><strong>Eliminates outdoor irrigation:</strong> the city runs a <a href="https://lascruces.gov/property/utilities/utility-services/water-conservation/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Water Conservation Program</a> focused on cutting outdoor water use. Synthetic turf removes the area entirely from the watering equation.</li><li><strong>Pairs with drip-irrigated borders:</strong> a turf-plus-planting-bed combo cuts outdoor water use 80% or more without turning the yard into rock.</li><li><strong>24-hour waste hotline:</strong> the city accepts water-waste reports at 575-528-4444. Synthetic turf keeps you off that radar.</li></ul><p class="cs-text cs-text-footer">Source: <a href="https://lascruces.gov/property/utilities/utility-services/water-conservation/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Las Cruces Utilities Water Conservation Program</a>.</p></div></section><section id="service-areas-825"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/fern.svg" height="483" width="224" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-fern"><div class="cs-container"><aside class="cs-info-card"><div class="cs-info-head"><span class="cs-topper"><span class="cs-topper-dot" aria-hidden=